data.description: Welcome to Seneca!  This property has been well cared for and is ready for a new owner.  Walking up to the home you can enjoy a lazy afternoon on your rocking chair front porch.  Stepping inside to the living room offers enough space for those game day Saturday's with your family and friends on your recently new carpet!  The kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space, GAS stove and Walk-in laundry room.  Need a backyard for that garden you wanted to start, this home has a perfect level lot with a shed.  Got a boat, the marina is close by to enjoy all those lake activities.  Come enjoy a evening downtown Seneca that offers plenty of restaurants, live music, Ram Cat alley and see why this is your next home.  USDA loan available with No money down!  Owner financing available with $10,000 down! Call for details
